title: [Delirium Manor, North Hallway]
description: Diminutive doors painted with whimsical gnomes, fairies, and one oversized two-headed troll, head off in all directions.  A more austere dark mahogany door with a tarnished brass knob sits ajar at the far end of the hallway.
paths: Obvious exits: northeast, east, southeast, south, southwest, west, northwest
